---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import aboutme from '../../assets/icons/aboutme.svg';
---

<section id='about' class='py-20 px-6'>
  <div class='max-w-[1440px] mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center'>
    <div class='flex justify-center'>
      <Image
        src={aboutme}
        alt='Illustration representing the developer'
        class='max-w-[500px] w-full'
      />
    </div>

    <div class='flex flex-col gap-6'>
      <h2 class='text-3xl md:text-4xl'>
        About <span class='font-extrabold'>Me</span>
      </h2>

      <p class='text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed'>
        I am a frontend developer focused on building modern, responsive, and
        user-friendly web applications. I enjoy transforming ideas into clean
        interfaces and smooth digital experiences.
      </p>

      <p class='text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed'>
        My main stack includes technologies such as JavaScript, TypeScript,
        Astro, React, and Tailwind CSS. I enjoy working on projects where
        performance, accessibility, and design all matter.
      </p>

      <p class='text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed'>
        Currently, I am improving my skills in full-stack development while
        building projects that help me grow as a developer.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
